text: Case Studies & Clients Nexora Technologies has built long-term relationships with clients across various sectors, ranging from startups to Fortune 500 enterprises. Below are some real-world examples of how we've helped businesses solve complex problems and drive measurable outcomes. Case Study 1: Quantum Fintech – Fraud Detection System Quantum Fintech, a US-based financial services firm, needed an intelligent system to flag suspicious transactions. Nexora built an AI-powered anomaly detection engine that analyzed transactional behavior patterns in real time. As a result, the client reduced fraud losses by 42% within six months. Case Study 2: GreenLogix Inc. – Logistics Optimization Platform GreenLogix, a Canadian logistics startup, was facing route inefficiencies and delivery delays. We developed a GPS-integrated dashboard that optimized delivery schedules using predictive analytics. The solution led to a 30% improvement in on-time deliveries and a 15% reduction in fuel costs. Case Study 3: EduBridge UK – E-learning Platform EduBridge approached us to build an interactive, multilingual learning management system (LMS). Our team created a responsive web app with gamification features and integrated Zoom APIs. The platform now supports 50,000+ learners and 1,000+ teachers globally.
